  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div data-mpa-action-id=\"mkf9n1vv1zj4\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"306\" data-backw=\"546\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/03KNO9Fib2w4gficvVhBKP6ic6h02Vxmrwd4m6AFH9oeIs09ibibYUjv82gn7ZWU8sjwzVbhROtOTqW08VpBibZ3b3cQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"307\" data-imgfileid=\"503374397\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.034em;width:100%;visibility:visible !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1100\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e9d36527&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w4gficvVhBKP6ic6h02Vxmrwd4m6AFH9oeIs09ibibYUjv82gn7ZWU8sjwzVbhROtOTqW08VpBibZ3b3cQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">来源丨APPSO</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">（ID：</span><span style=\"outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">appsolution</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">）</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">图源丨Midjourney</span></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd21ia\">上个月你刚花 20 美元订阅了 ChatGPT Plus，转头这个月朋友圈就被「Claude 秒杀一切」刷屏，再过一个月可能又换成「Gemini 吊打一切」。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1i7b\">看着每月的账单，你难免开始怀疑人生：这 AI 会员，开不完，真的开不完？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1y15\">这并非你的错觉，知名大模型竞技场 LMArena.ai 分析了自 2023 年年中以来的模型排名榜单，撕开大模型行业最残酷的一面：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder __bg_gif\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"307\" data-backw=\"546\" data-imgfileid=\"503593374\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f43406f1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FePTzepwoNWMlGFvVPBBT3uxXzBUEtX9Cyu1BO8RSr65QJnpiax2k2HCA6SG1Nz1W5PsqKAjBFsB6zV4caicGQSIQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D0\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd59w\">排名第一的模型平均只能保持约 35 天的领先地位，通常情况下会在 5 个月内跌出前五名，在 7 个月内跌出前十名。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1xzb\">而曾经一战封神的榜首模型 OpenAI o1 目前排在第 56 位，Claude 3 Opus 更是跌到了第 139 位。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"303\" data-backw=\"546\" data-imgfileid=\"503593375\" data-ratio=\"0.5546296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6f8080a7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePTzepwoNWMlGFvVPBBT3uxXzBUEtX9CeaFbAApmV3DW837Jp4zE6MXEq7A5NLticuOpvPkzDjItR11VLtHob4g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D1\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vdyer\">虽然 LMArena.ai 的这份榜单本身可能存在注水空间，但这种剧烈洗牌依然反映了 AI 模型过气速度之快，35 天正在成为顶级 AI 模型的「斩杀线」。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"45\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"502705851\" data-ratio=\"0.07777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d0e93a19&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zPEErlmM1icwAxnc0Bfu3icv2I49pcxADF7lYww8vNML5TkajhGu2m1NA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9obew1qh7\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkf9obf71vzq\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">亿级投流</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9obew1qh7\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkf9obf71vzq\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">换不来 AI 用户的「回头率」</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1k19\">过去两年，你一定有看到过互联网上流传的这张梗图。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"442\" data-backw=\"546\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/ePTzepwoNWMlGFvVPBBT3uxXzBUEtX9CJZibZ8qpG32cjo2nqb9icrKQf5OkKYnkWdGiae45RnLrn167ULCTQzGDw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"637.6642335766422\" data-cropy1=\"29.197080291970806\" data-cropy2=\"545.4014598540147\" data-imgfileid=\"503593378\" data-ratio=\"0.8100470957613815\" style=\"width:100%;background-color:transparent;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"637\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=475713c7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePTzepwoNWMlGFvVPBBT3uxXzBUEtX9CKaT7NibRv9u5AibuKd0dbhAo9Iib3bLnWDIgiciboJIR6eeR5nGibu2oyibYA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%23imgIndex%3D2\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1sb5\">去年年初还是 ChatGPT 独领风骚，随后 DeepSeek、Claude 轮番坐庄，如今 Gemini 又异军突起。无论 2025 还是 2026 年，影响用户选择模型最核心的因素依旧是性能至上。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd17rr\">用户的选择从来纯粹，哪款模型好用、顺手，便会坚定不移地投向其怀抱，不得不承认的是，现在的 AI 用户，从一开始就没有忠诚可言。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1atr\">比如 Sora 2 刚发布时被吹捧为短视频的降维打击，5 天内下载量破百万，但 a16z 合伙人 Olivia Moore 抛出的数据却显示，用户的 30 天留存率仅 1%，60 天直接归零。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"258\" data-backw=\"546\" data-imgfileid=\"503592042\" data-ratio=\"0.4722222222222222\" style=\"width:100%;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:transparent;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b7cfdf79&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePTzepwoNWM4slhXOhNsZI9YMEX6x8Tqsx06gWjwkJnjd4dg6qS3oGry7beueurXfoqgmRfm7onIXIEvFEBKXw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D3\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1x3j\">如果把视野转回国内，大模型战火叙事同样残酷：AI 应用月投流规模动辄千万甚至十亿级，但除了尝到初期的流量甜头，用户留存率同样惨不忍睹。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd18d9\">而这种「始乱终弃」的现象绕不开因 AI 热潮催生的「FOMO」心理——大量所谓的 AI 游客只是为了跟上潮流、探索新鲜工具，但在体验过后转身离开。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1l5m\">深究根源，多数 AI 产品至今未能搭建起留住用户的闭环。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1yg7\">在过去的 SaaS 行业，「因 X 而来，因 Y 而留」是奉为圭臬的增长逻辑。就像有人最初用 Canva 做社交海报，但后来却被品牌素材包、模板库和团队协作功能绑住，成为长期用户。亦或者很多人第一次点开微信视频号，就是因为朋友圈、群聊里的一次顺手转发。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vdwyx\">内容本身未必惊艳，但它被包裹在熟人关系之中。你可以不关心视频讲了什么，但很难对谁转了这条、谁在下面留言视而不见。点赞除了给创作者，也是为了维持关系的连接。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd2r\">但这套逻辑在多数 AI 产品身上彻底失灵。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"307\" data-backw=\"546\" data-imgfileid=\"503593386\" data-ratio=\"0.562037037037037\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dbdf1641&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePTzepwoNWMlGFvVPBBT3uxXzBUEtX9Cf83WlkfekgQuJJovFvlQciaXgX8vdgGSn00eJjIO7iaUNDcyQtOiau58w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D4\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd96t\">最典型的就是 Sora 2，即便能生成真假难辨的视频，但若没有原生社区支撑用户分享、互动、收获反馈，它终究只是个孤立工具——没除了极少数专业人士，大多数普通用户往往缺乏长期使用的需求。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1gep\">除此之外，重度用户的使用逻辑也在发生变化。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1757\">英伟达 CEO 黄仁勋就曾在公开场合分享自己的 AI 使用秘籍：从不依赖单一模型，而是将同一个问题同时抛给多个 AI，让它们互相参考、交叉验证，以此提升回答质量与可信度。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"364\" data-backw=\"546\" data-imgfileid=\"503593380\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=320323ab&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePTzepwoNWMlGFvVPBBT3uxXzBUEtX9CgwB2vMibkl5jKf2c75B0jnb7tmY99Dclaa5NiaZzHy3Cef8y06wKNPgA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D5\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vdp0n\">这背后的逻辑不难理解：当下没有哪个模型能赢家通吃，不同模型各有优势。时至今日，ChatGPT 已不再是 AI 唯一入口，用 Claude 写长文本、Gemini 写代码、多模型协作取长补短才是常态。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1zf7\">尤为关键的是，巨头们早已手握成熟的生态闭环，只需将 AI 能力无缝嵌入其中，便能坐享生态红利。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vdgos\">Google 手握一整套已经被验证过二十年的入口体系，能够将 Gemini 能够无缝嵌入 &nbsp;YouTube、Workspace 办公套件，更深度绑定 Chrome、地图等核心流量入口，同时开放 API 拉拢海量开发者。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"364\" data-backw=\"546\" data-imgfileid=\"503593385\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7eebfa32&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePTzepwoNWMlGFvVPBBT3uxXzBUEtX9CmBlZ9S4ooh04hyp4U9hLq5dvh7DSBrmGrpyAXicu75VibUUic41mACAqQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D6\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vdu6p\">这种润物细无声的渠道分发，能够让 Gemini 轻松收割海量的普通用户与企业客户，也让 ChatGPT 用户反复摇摆。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vdl8b\">面对用户使用意图薄弱、迁移成本近乎为零的困境，OpenAI 为代表的初创厂商一方面不断加筑功能防线：绑定生态厂商合作，推出 AI Office、AI 浏览器、AI 群聊等产品。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"315\" data-backw=\"546\" data-imgfileid=\"503593381\" data-ratio=\"0.5777777777777777\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=799d5e17&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePTzepwoNWMlGFvVPBBT3uxXzBUEtX9C6iaJaawiaBnIlzGAVAdNAzJWMsNpHnDgrib010YTnW4CCOnaZOOJBicrIg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D7\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1iq0\">用 Sam Altman 的话说，这是为了发挥 AI 最大生产力，一切都值得用 AI 重做一遍，但换个角度看，这也是入口焦虑下的被动选择。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vdx2t\">另一方面，OpenAI 也在 C 端加码押注「个性化记忆」与情商——允许用户让模型跨会话记住写作风格、专业术语等偏好，还能手动编辑记忆库；针对心理咨询等场景优化语气，本质上就是希望通过个性化功能和「情感绑定」来抬高用户迁移门槛。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1fvu\">但这些煞费苦心的防御招式，短时间终究还是难以逆转用户流失的大趋势。当产品端的突破变得举步维艰，于是也有许多厂商将目光投向了更「省时省力」的赛道——在衡量行业性能地位的榜单上动起了歪脑筋。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"45\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"502705850\" data-ratio=\"0.07777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9f561975&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zSsWdBUSJRaL8xxhHssPefRrhSRCKFFTvyO0oNl4HVrDTxA2PCXqv1g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9pnau6kf\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkf9pnb8jox\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">我可以随时换</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9pnau6kf\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkf9pnb8jox\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">我也应该随时换</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vdqdi\">前文提到的 35 天斩杀线，核心是参考 LMArena 反映的行业趋势，但需要指出的是，即便是这份被视作相对权威的评测榜单，本身也暗藏不少猫腻。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd17s2\">Meta 此前被曝出的刷榜行为，直接扯下了这份权威榜单的遮羞布。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vdm4l\">发布 Llama 4 前，Meta 私下测试了 27 个变体版本，却只将分数最高的」特供版「公之于众，靠着这套玩法，Llama 4 一度霸榜。但当面向公众的正式版发布后，排名瞬间从第 2 名暴跌至第 32 名，滤镜破碎一览无余。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"307\" data-backw=\"546\" data-imgfileid=\"503593382\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=74b34683&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePTzepwoNWMlGFvVPBBT3uxXzBUEtX9CSxZRt3ZodFkkV6nibKtCibibOyAUGyzDF8GxIqia2QaWWw5GVQAKs39IsA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D8\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1uk0\">榜单的评测机制本身也存在不少问题，其理论上是这么运作的：用户输入提示，比较两个 AI 回应，然后选出更好的一个。实际情况却是：随机网民匆匆扫一眼，用两秒钟点击他们感觉还不错的选项。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd17i0\">Surge AI 在《LMArena is a cancer on AI》一文中曾指出，竞技场中 52% 的对决判定存在错误，大众投票更偏爱回答冗长、排版华丽甚至带表情包的「显眼包」。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1z8\">很多时候，AI 只要自信地胡说八道，就能轻松击败诚实却枯燥的对手。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vdgux\">当刷榜作弊成为 AI 行业的潜规则，用户对模型的信任也在不断被透支。再加上模型们隔三差五出现的「降智」更新，用户对「榜一大哥」的祛魅，显然也只是时间问题。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"348\" data-backw=\"546\" data-imgfileid=\"503593384\" data-ratio=\"0.6370370370370371\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3d700340&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePTzepwoNWMlGFvVPBBT3uxXzBUEtX9ClVcVjFTJBaRSMSzibLuksablJCwjlTenwSxKjGYd0IHHiby2j7q9ra4Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D9\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vdyw8\">而开源与低价的崛起，则进一步冲击了行业格局。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vdob6\">微软基于内部数据的研究显示，DeepSeek R1 极大推动了全球大多数地区的 AI 普及，在白俄罗斯拿下 56% 的份额，古巴 49%、俄罗斯 43%，即便是埃塞俄比亚和津巴布韦，份额也分别达到 18% 和 17%。</span></p>\n    <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n     <div data-pm-slice=\"2 5 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">\n      <p style=\"margin-left:16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"388\" data-backw=\"546\" data-imgfileid=\"503593383\" data-ratio=\"0.7111111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9df3db04&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePTzepwoNWMlGFvVPBBT3uxXzBUEtX9CYHd6tm0HFxBJtM6p0pZr6gVhWccza4ECpV2dBu2XokD5ic6YUDQLibKg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D10\"></p>\n      <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n       <div>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9q6nog64\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkf9q6nz11kn\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图片来自金融时报</span></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1zgk\">原因并不复杂，甚至可以说相当朴素：价格屠夫。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vdxe9\">对于绝大多数人来说，免费模型已经覆盖了大多数日常需求，用户就会很自然地进入另一种心态：我可以随时换，我也应该随时换。对于开发者而言，即便 OpenAI 等巨头多次大幅降价，其每 Token 收费依旧遥遥领先于 DeepSeek。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1195\">此外，开发者还基于 Qwen、DeepSeek 等开源模型，针对教育、医疗等细分场景做轻量化微调，诞生了一批「小而美」的垂直模型。它们虽在通用榜单分数不高，但特定场景表现远超闭源巨头，进一步瓦解了头部模型的话语权。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1b1z\">在这样的背景下，那些卡在中间地带的 AI 玩家反而最为尴尬：既不够强，也不够便宜，却还寄希望于刷榜、讲故事维持存在感。在「35 天生死线」面前，他们几乎没有回旋空间。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkf9n1vd1os8\">等待他们的结局，便只有迟早被斩杀。</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
